# Implementation Plan - Complete HRMS API v3.0 Secured

This plan outlines the steps to build a comprehensive, secure, and multi-tenant HRMS API using AdonisJS, based on the provided SQL schema.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> - **Encryption**: Sensitive PII fields (Salary, Bank Account, PAN) will be encrypted at the application layer using AdonisJS Encryption provider.
> - **Soft Deletes**: All critical tables will implement soft deletion logic.
> - **Multi-Tenancy**: `org_id` will be enforced in all queries via a Global Macro or Base Model.

## Proposed Changes

### [Core Infrastructure]

#### [MODIFY] [BaseModel](file:///d:/HRMS_Backend/HRMS_BACKEND/apps/backend/app/Models/BaseModel.ts) (New or Modify existing)
- Implement `SoftDeletes` functionality.
- Add hooks for `AuditLogging`.

### [Authentication & Security]

#### [MODIFY] [AuthController.ts](file:///d:/HRMS_Backend/HRMS_BACKEND/apps/backend/app/Controllers/Http/AuthController.ts)
- Add endpoints for `ForgotPassword`, `ResetPassword`, `VerifyEmail`.
- Implement `2FA` flow using `OtpTokens`.
- Add `MagicLink` login support.

#### [NEW] [InvitationsController.ts](file:///d:/HRMS_Backend/HRMS_BACKEND/apps/backend/app/Controllers/Http/InvitationsController.ts)
- Manage employee invitations (Invite, Accept, Revoke).

#### [NEW] [SecurityController.ts](file:///d:/HRMS_Backend/HRMS_BACKEND/apps/backend/app/Controllers/Http/SecurityController.ts)
- Manage `IP Whitelist` and `API Rate Limits`.

### [Billing & Subscriptions]

